text:
User settings

To create new user
influx user create -n &lt;username&gt; -p &lt;password&gt; -o &lt;org-name&gt; 
influx user create -n ben -p Asdf,mnb1234 -o phisaver


To show user list
influx user ls


To delete user
influx user delete -i &lt;id&gt;


To delete user
influx user update -i &lt;user-id&gt; -n &lt;new-username&gt;
